      "content": "it just feels like the \"small steps\" are too much. every tiny thing is heavy. i look at my life and there's nothing left. no hobbies, no friends i want to see, nothing. it feels like i'm just a ghost walking around in a body that won't stop functioning. why does it have to keep going like this?",
